    			<h2>Bespoke Tour of Iolani Palace: Royal Grounds</h2>
    			<p><span>Cultural/Guided Tour + Private Dining, Honolulu, HI</span>Built in 1882 and home to Hawaiian royalty, the palace plays an integral part in understanding the history and culture of Hawaii. Painstakingly restored, the building hosts beautiful ornate decor. It is only palace which exists in the US borders. Following their one-hour guided tour, guests can retire to one of the ground's tranquil lawns for a private lunch.</p>
    		</div>
