    			<p><span>Yachting/Sailing, Kapolei, HI</span>Guests take to the high seas with the choice of two bespoke experiences on board a luxury yacht. By day, guests can soak up the sun and sights and hit the water for snorkeling sessions, while others can opt to set sail as the sun sets and enjoy a sumptuous supper.</p>
    		</div>
        </article>
        <article style="background: url('images/11.jpg')">
