    			<h2>Submarine Expedition</h2>
    			<p><span>Underwater/Adventure, Honolulu, HI</span>A truly unique experience, guests will embark on a tour 100 foot below water on board the world's largest high-tech submarine to observe Hawaii's spectacular ocean life. Green turtles, stingrays and even sharks can be viewed on this unforgettable 1.5 hour adventure.</p>
    		</div>
        </article>
        <article style="background: url('images/13.jpg')">
