    			<p><span>Cultural/Relaxation, Kaneohe, HI</span>Guests are treated to the very best of Oahu with a curated day trip, encompassing the most stunning beaches, the legendary Diamond Head Lookout and a delicious leisurely lunch at the picturesque Haiku Gardens, before taking in downtown historical sites of importance, including Washington Place.</p>
